they're going to burn me alive.

149
00:09:36,375 --> 00:09:37,944
[SPEAKING JAPANESE]

150
00:09:40,413 --> 00:09:42,748
What did you say, you rotten
son of a bitch?

151
00:09:42,782 --> 00:09:44,784
[WOMEN GASPING]

152
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:55,161
Thank you.

153
00:09:57,763 --> 00:09:59,865
