cuffs off--

160
00:10:05,938 --> 00:10:07,039
- I'll kick your ass, man. -
--so I can print you.

161
00:10:07,073 --> 00:10:07,907
Ha ha! I'll kill you.

162
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:08,674
