167
00:10:13,212 --> 00:10:14,313
I don't think so!

168
00:10:14,347 --> 00:10:15,014
I don't know what the hell
you're talking about, man.

169
00:10:15,047 --> 00:10:15,881
- Come on! - Hey, how about it?

170
00:10:15,915 --> 00:10:17,683
You guys can't-- you can't do
that.

171
00:10:17,717 --> 00:10:18,417
[LAUGHING]

172
00:10:18,451 --> 00:10:20,820
Hey, you can't do that!

173
00:10:20,853 --> 00:10:21,787
[THUDDING]

174
00:10:21,821 --> 00:10:24,223
What the hell do you think
you're doing?

175
00:10:24,256 --> 00:10:26,292
Give it up!

176
00:10:26,325 --> 00:10:27,994
Could you direct me to Tom's
office?

177
00:10:28,027 --> 00:10:28,928
Tom?

178
00:10:28,961 --> 00:10:30,029
Who's Tom?

179
00:10:30,062 --> 00:10:31,297
Chief Tom Bradfield.

180
00:10:31,330 --> 00:10:32,231
Yeah.

181
00:10:32,264 --> 00:10:33,366
Chief's office is upstairs.

182
00:10:33,399 --> 00:10:34,300
Hey.

183
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:35,401
Thank you.

184
00:10:35,434 --> 00:10:38,070
