185
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,041
[GRUNTING]

186
00:10:43,409 --> 00:10:46,379
[OFFICER PANTING]

187
00:10:57,857 --> 00:10:58,824
RIO: Oh.

188
00:10:58,858 --> 00:10:59,759
